4hwy1665703203214.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hwy1665703203214.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hwy1665703203214.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hwy1665703203214\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the component instance to serve as the SAX handler.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__topic_d136346e1_d136347e1_d136348e1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__codeblock_fkn_brg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">SETHANDLER(Instance)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__section_ywf_crg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d466140e56\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">SETHANDLER parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Instance</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_d16280e1_d16281e1_d16282e1__entry__4\">Name of the component instance that handles SAX\n                        callback operations.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__section_lgj_hrg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d466140e117\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">SETHANDLER return values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb__entry__1\">Number</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb__entry__2\">Error</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb__entry__1\">–59</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb__entry__2\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_OPERATION&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hwy1665703203214__table_hn4_jrg_hwb__entry__3\">No callback operation can be found.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__section_z4b_nrg_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d466140e168\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__p_d136361e1_d136362e1_d136363e1\">This operation must be activated prior to calling\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__p_d136364e1_d136365e1_d136366e1\">A valid handler component must implement at least\n            one of the supported callback operations. Otherwise, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SETHANDLER</span>\n            returns an error.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hwy1665703203214_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__codeblock_tzv_prg_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">activate $50.setHandler($instancename)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hwy1665703203214__p_d136367e1_d136368e1_d136369e1\">This will set the current component instance as the\n            SAX handler instance.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528409\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528409\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SETHANDLER Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the component instance to serve as the SAX handler. SETHANDLER(Instance) Copy Parameters Table 1. SETHANDLER parameters Parameter Data Type Direction Description Instance String IN Name of the component instance that handles SAX callback operations. Return Values Table 2. SETHANDLER return values Number Error Description –59 <UACTERR_NO_OPERATION> No callback operation can be found. Description This operation must be activated prior to calling PARSE or PARSEFILE . A valid handler component must implement at least one of the supported callback operations. Otherwise, SETHANDLER returns an error. Explain this code activate $50.setHandler($instancename) Copy This will set the current component instance as the SAX handler instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}